avdta.dta

Class VehicleRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.dta.VehicleRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<VehicleRecord>

    public class VehicleRecord
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<VehicleRecord>
    This represents an entry in the demand file, and is used to easily manipulate data associated with individual vehicle trips.
